contentrichtext.text: '''Wake Forest''' may refer to: * [[Wake Forest, North Carolina]], a town near Raleigh, North Carolina * [[Wake Forest University]], a university founded in the above town and now located in Winston-Salem, North Carolina * Wake Forest, name of the plantation owned by [[Calvin Jones (physician)]] that became the first home of Wake Forest University * [[Wake Forest Demon Deacons]], athletic teams from Wake Forest University ==See also== * [[Lake Forest College]], a college located in [[Lake Forest, Illinois]] {{geodis}}
